          "returnType": "Collider",
          "description": "Attach a collider to this body. Accepts a Collider instance or its ColliderOptions (a convenience that constructs the collider for you). When the body is already in a world, the collider is id-allocated, registered, the mass model is recomputed and the world geometry synchronised immediately; on a free-standing body the collider is simply held until world.add(). Returns the collider."
